data.title: Freiburg im Breisgau (English)
data.meta_description: Freiburg im Breisgau Freiburg is a city in Breisgau, Baden-Württemberg, Germany, on the western edge of the Black Forest. The hottest temperature ever recorded in Germany was here at 39C (query?)
